{"title":"Radar Roundup: Amigo Hippy Trucker Hat, Wolf Tooth GRX 12 Speed, Crank Brothers Stamp 1 Gen 2, ENVE Foundation Price Drop, Hudski Doggler Sale, and Seven Majors","link":"https://theradavist.com/radar-roundup-amigo-hippie-trucker-hat-wolf-tooth-grx-12-speed-crank-brothers-stamp-1-gen-2-enve-foundation-price-drop-hudski-doggler-sale-and-seven-majors/","date":1694599208000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2160\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?w=2160&amp;quality=75 2160w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Our Radar Roundup compiles products and videos from the ‘net in an easy-to-digest format. Read on below for today’s findings…<span></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/MG_2289_1024x1024%402x.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt /><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/MG_2296_1024x1024%402x.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://amigoframeworks.com/products/hippy-trucker-mesh-back-hat\" target=\"_blank\">Amigo Frameworks “Hippy” Trucker Hat</a> $35</h3>\n<p>When you and Ralph are buggin’ out, sittin’ round the campfire in the desert of Nevada outside of Las Vegas after Ralph’s ESP wasn’t as sharp as you expected, causing you to lose your life’s savings of Bitcoin at the Black Jack table, forever stranding you on Earth, sometimes ya just gotta look at Ralph, with his green/grey pallette and proclaim: “Let’s become hippy truckers!”</p>\n<p>Ralph, being an extraterrestrial from Tleilax, knows a thing or two about truckin’, so you two buy a long hauler (with a bike rack of course) and begin making runs for the green chile cartels of New Mexico. Each run you make a pit stop in Roswell to do a quick road ride, grabbing your “Hippy” Trucker Hat, and cruise around on magestic, vacant roadways.</p>\n<p>You might never make enough money slingin’ chile. Not enough to vacate Earth for Tleilax, but sometimes, the cool wind blowing across your receding hairline is enough to make you cherish this ever-warming rock of a planet we call home.</p>\n<p>In stock now for $35, or about half a bushel of New Mexico green chile, at <a href=\"https://amigoframeworks.com/products/hippy-trucker-mesh-back-hat\" target=\"_blank\">Amigo Frameworks</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/WT_GR8_110_BCD_44T_FT_BLK_01_120.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/WT_GR8_110_BCD_44T_FT_BLK_01_120.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/WT_GR8_110_BCD_44T_FT_BLK_01_120.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/WT_GR8_110_BCD_44T_FT_BLK_01_120.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/WT_GR8_110_BCD_44T_FT_BLK_01_120.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/WT_GR8_110_BCD_44T_FT_BLK_01_120.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/110GR4-R-S-00F-40_1200x.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/110GR4-R-S-00F-40_1200x.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/110GR4-R-S-00F-40_1200x.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/110GR4-R-S-00F-40_1200x.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/110GR4-R-S-00F-40_1200x.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/110GR4-R-S-00F-40_1200x.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/collections/gravel-cyclocross-road/products/110-bcd-asymmetric-4-bolt-for-shimano-grx-cranks?variant=40107944017955&amp;utm_source=Klaviyo&amp;utm_medium=campaign&amp;utm_campaign=GRX%2012-Speed%20Chainring%20Launch&amp;_kx=o3de4cOlLUke0dqtXR763lFhNIz9gKuKFgxx6cWZF8Y%3D.UyKAxr\" target=\"_blank\">Wolf Tooth Drop-Stop ST Chainrings for Shimano GRX</a> $84.95</h3>\n<p>Good news! Wolf Tooth’s Drop-Stop rings for the all-new Shimano GRX kit are available. Bad news! Only in sizes that Shimano currently offers. Good news! Other chainring sizes (36, 38, 46-52t) will be on the way soon. We’ll update you here as events warrant but if you were looking for a 40-44t ring for GRX 12 Speed, now’s your chance!</p>\n<p>Roll on over to <a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/collections/gravel-cyclocross-road/products/110-bcd-asymmetric-4-bolt-for-shimano-grx-cranks?variant=40107944017955&amp;utm_source=Klaviyo&amp;utm_medium=campaign&amp;utm_campaign=GRX%2012-Speed%20Chainring%20Launch&amp;_kx=o3de4cOlLUke0dqtXR763lFhNIz9gKuKFgxx6cWZF8Y%3D.UyKAxr\" target=\"_blank\">Wolf Tooth</a> for more.</p>\n<p><em>Check out Josh’s initial reaction to Shimano GRX: <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/shimano-grx-12-speed-gravel-group-review/\" target=\"_blank\">First Ride Review: Introducing Shimano GRX Mechanical 12-Speed Components</a></em></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1786\" height=\"1250\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/unnamed-4_121222.png?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/unnamed-4_121222.png?w=1786&amp;quality=75 1786w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/unnamed-4_121222.png?resize=1024,717&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/unnamed-4_121222.png?resize=768,538&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/unnamed-4_121222.png?resize=1335,934&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/unnamed-4_121222.png?resize=700,490&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/unnamed-4_121222.png?resize=1536,1075&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3>Crank Brothers Stamp 1 Gen 2 Pedals <a href=\"https://www.crankbrothers.com/collections/stamp/products/stamp-1-gen-2-large\" target=\"_blank\">Large</a> and <a href=\"https://www.crankbrothers.com/collections/stamp/products/stamp-1-gen-2-small\" target=\"_blank\">Small</a> $59.99</h3>\n<p>Like Star Trek, the next generation of Crank Brothers Stamp 1 pedals are better than the original in every way. Available in both large and small platforms, now featuring a<span> true concave body design for keeping your feet planted on those new, one-piece pin design, and trusted Igus internal components for durability, the Gen 2 Stamp 1 has all you need and more in an array of colors and affordable-ish pricepoint. </span></p>\n<p>Check out Crankbrothers for the <a href=\"https://www.crankbrothers.com/collections/stamp/products/stamp-1-gen-2-large\" target=\"_blank\">Large</a> and <a href=\"https://www.crankbrothers.com/collections/stamp/products/stamp-1-gen-2-small\" target=\"_blank\">Small</a> specs.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" hei