st.com/uploads/2023/09/AM30_Hero-2400x0-c-default.png?resize=1335,1068&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/AM30_Hero-2400x0-c-default.png?resize=700,560&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/AM30_Hero-2400x0-c-default.png?resize=1536,1229&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/AM30_Hero-2400x0-c-default.png?resize=2048,1638&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/AG28_Hero-2400x0-c-default.png?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/AG28_Hero-2400x0-c-default.png?w=2400&amp;quality=75 2400w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/AG28_Hero-2400x0-c-default.png?resize=1024,819&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/AG28_Hero-2400x0-c-default.png?resize=2000,1600&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/AG28_Hero-2400x0-c-default.png?resize=768,614&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/AG28_Hero-2400x0-c-default.png?resize=1800,1440&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/AG28_Hero-2400x0-c-default.png?resize=1335,1068&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/AG28_Hero-2400x0-c-default.png?resize=700,560&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/AG28_Hero-2400x0-c-default.png?resize=1536,1229&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/AG28_Hero-2400x0-c-default.png?resize=2048,1638&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.enve.com/product-category/wheels/\" target=\"_blank\">ENVE’s New USA-Made Foundation Wheel Pricing is Wild</a> $1,400</h3>\n<p>It doesn’t matter if you’re from a road, gravel, or mountain house, $1,400 for US-made carbon wheels is cheap! ENVE’s Foundation line began as a means to offer a more affordable US-made carbon wheelset and the brand just announced even lower pricing down from $1,600.</p>\n<p>So if you’re looking for some aero road wheels, durable gravel hoops, or all-mountain hops, roll on over to <a href=\"https://www.enve.com/product-category/wheels/\" target=\"_blank\">ENVE</a> to check out the new pricing.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/Hudski-Doggler-Review-6.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/Hudski-Doggler-Review-6.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/Hudski-Doggler-Review-6.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/Hudski-Doggler-Review-6.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/Hudski-Doggler-Review-6.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/Hudski-Doggler-Review-6.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/Hudski-Doggler-Review-6.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/Hudski-Doggler-Review-6.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://hudskibikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Hudski Doggler Sale</a> $1400/$1540</h3>\n<p>Hybrid bikes ain’t nothin’ to f’ with. Hybrid bikes ain’t nothin’ to f’ with. The Hudski Doggler is re-inventing the hybrid ATB and now, you can score one of these all-rounders for hundreds less than when John’s review was posted. Sorry guys, we should have timed that better. Oh well, save now on the Doggler City/Gravel/Mountain at <a href=\"https://hudskibikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Hudski Bikes</a>!</p>\n<p><em>If you haven’t read John’s review, don’t miss it: <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/hudski-doggler-review/\" target=\"_blank\">Hybrid Moments: A Hudski Doggler Review</a></em></p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<div><span><span>﻿</span>﻿</span><span>﻿</span></div>\n<p> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_w6qynvFZtA\" target=\"_blank\">Seven Majors</a></h3>\n<p>Three riders, seven mountains, 24 hours. Can they do it? Why are they doing it? Wouldn’t you rather go to the beach?</p>\n<p>Yes, it’s the adventure of the summer, the Forever Outsiders spirit, an unforgettable experience with a little bit of a laugh (and maybe some tears). Their reward? A cappuccino, a blueberry tart and some very sore legs. Oh, and the glory of uploading it to Strava.</p>\n<p>Starring : Col de la Bonette (2715 m), Col de Vars (2108 m), Col d’Izoard (2360 m), Col Agnel (2744 m), Col de Sampeyre (2284 m), Col de Fauniera (2481m), Col de Lombarde (2350 m).</p>\n<p>Excellent work, <a href=\"https://www.cafeducycliste.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Cafe Du Cycliste</a>!</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Radavision</h3>\n<p>Stuff we see on the ‘net that causes pause…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2160\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?w=2160&amp;quality=75 2160w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/09/RR0913_071054.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><em>Photo by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CxDBkJfPWYF/\" target=\"_blank\">@blissfieldphoto</a></em></p>\n<p>Sometimes the simplest vignettes evoke the most profound scenery. Well done!</p>\n<p><em>If you’d like your photo featured in our Radar Roundup posts, tag us <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/theradavist/\" target=\"_blank\">on Instagram</a>!</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/radar-roundup-amigo-hippie-trucker-hat-wolf-tooth-grx-12-speed-crank-brothers-stamp-1-gen-2-enve-foundation-price-drop-hudski-doggler-sale-and-seven-majors/\">Radar Roundup: Amigo Hippy Trucker Hat, Wolf Tooth GRX 12 Speed, Crank Brothers Stamp 1 Gen 2, ENVE Foundation Price Drop, Hudski Doggler Sale, and Seven Majors</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"1fde9fad568cc03f55be306316f90ef16629b51f42518b718d77005d23399254","category":"Cycling"}